headline: SouthTrust Bank Selects Jack Henry to Fuel Growth and Innovation
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced today that SouthTrust Bank has selected Jack Henry to modernize its technology infrastructure, enabling the bank to differentiate, streamline operations, and more aggressively pursue growth.
